not to be left out.

17
00:04:03.232 --> 00:04:05.276
You look incredible.

18
00:04:05.944 --> 00:04:08.259
Yeah, but we have to hurry.

19
00:04:23.797 --> 00:04:25.819
I prefer this one.

20
00:04:28.927 --> 00:04:30.303
Right.

21
00:04:58.042 --> 00:04:59.919
