22
00:05:00.128 --> 00:05:02.379
<i>This way. This way, please.</i>

23
00:05:03.423 --> 00:05:05.196
<i>This way, please.</i>

24
00:05:06.031 --> 00:05:07.595
<i>One more.</i>

25
00:05:11.640 --> 00:05:14.434
